Alain De Bot
============

SETUP
-----

  migration.rb

will create the sqlite database you require

INGEST
------

running

  ingest.rb

once a week will add the latest de botton tweets.

GENERATION
----------

  generate.rb

will generate a hundred initial tweets. Thereafter, the system ought to stock up if it's low.


RUNNING
-------

  alaindebot.rb

should be called by cron once every X minutes
